  "description": "<p><strong>近日一位名为Brandyn White的开发者成功为Google Glass研发了全新虚拟现实交互界面，并在未来某一天让Glass软件能够更好的现实生活相互交融。</strong>本次展示的交互界面基于Mirror API基础上搭建，整体界面非常的友善，可通过Android的APKs进行直接推送。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ec1e269/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244969.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E6%9B%B4%E5%8F%8B%E5%96%84+%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8EMirror+API%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244969.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E6%9B%B4%E5%8F%8B%E5%96%84+%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8EMirror+API%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244969.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E6%9B%B4%E5%8F%8B%E5%96%84+%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8EMirror+API%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244969.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E6%9B%B4%E5%8F%8B%E5%96%84+%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8EMirror+API%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.fee