  "description": "<p>最近一次听说Griffin的PowerDock 5充电座的消息，还是在今年的CES展会上。<strong>今天，该公司终于推出了这款新产品，能够通过5个USB接口为包括平板电脑在内的多个设备进行充电。</strong>为了方便设备的摆放，PowerDock 5充电座的上方还特地设置了5个槽位的透明隔板(托架)，使用者大可放心地把他们的iPad等大小伙伴都摆上去。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ec1e267/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244968.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%BE%8E%E6%B9%83%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%9AGriffin%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BAPower+Dock+5%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%A3USB%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E5%BA%A7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244968.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%BE%8E%E6%B9%83%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%9AGriffin%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BAPower+Dock+5%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%A3USB%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E5%BA%A7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244968.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%BE%8E%E6%B9%83%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%9AGriffin%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BAPower+Dock+5%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%A3USB%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E5%BA%A7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244968.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%BE%8E%E6%B9%83%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%9AGriffin%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BAPower+Dock+5%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%A3USB%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E5%BA%A7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244968.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%BE%