  "date": "Wed, 17 Jul 2013 01:05:58 GMT", 
  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/244946.htm", 
  "description": "<p>自PRISM项目曝光之外，微软等多家知名科技公司都被认定为主动参与了公民个人数据分享活动。<strong>不过，微软对这一说法一直持否定态度，今天它又再次发表博文来重申自己的立场，并指出政府已经严重妨碍到其享有的分享信息给民众的宪法权利。</strong>虽然微软现在还在等待司法部长的最终决定，但这家公司仍透露，自己将会尽可能地把更多、更详细的信息公布于众。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ec170e3/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244946.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E4%BB%8E%E6%9C%AA%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%87%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244946.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E4%BB%8E%E6%9C%AA%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%87%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244946.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E4%BB%8E%E6%9C%AA%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%87%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244946.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E4%BB%8E%E6%9C%AA%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%87%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a